description: List the Packages that are associated with an Image Build Version, as determined by Amazon Web Services Systems Manager Inventory at build time.

parameters.name: imageBuildVersionArn
parameters.description: Filter results for the ListImagePackages request by the Image Build Version ARN.

nested_items.name: requestId
nested_items.description: The request ID that uniquely identifies this request.

nested_items.name: imagePackageList
nested_items.description: The list of Image Packages returned in the response.

nested_items.name: packageName
nested_items.description: The name of the package that's reported to the operating system package manager.

nested_items.name: packageVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the package that's reported to the operating system package manager.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.
